  <brief_title>SI-613 Study for Knee Osteoarthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Repeated Intra-Articular Injection of SI-613 in Patients With Osteoarthritis of the Knee</official_title>
